    helpText: 'Properly securing your home and delegating responsibilities provides peace of mind and prevents issues that could disrupt your trip or require emergency return. Contact your post office to hold mail, arrange pet care or plant watering with trusted friends or services, notify your home security system of your absence, and confirm work coverage for urgent matters. Create a detailed instruction sheet for each person helping you and exchange contact information for any questions that arise during your trip.'
  },
  {
    id: 'prompt-43',
    prompt: 'Create and share a complete travel itinerary with emergency contacts including accommodation details, transportation confirmations, and daily schedules',
    category: 'action',
    helpText: 'Sharing your detailed itinerary with trusted contacts creates a crucial safety network and enables quick assistance if emergencies arise during your travels. Compile all confirmation numbers, addresses, phone numbers, and daily plans into a single document, then share it with 2-3 close contacts who can reach authorities or assist remotely if needed. This comprehensive itinerary serves as both a safety measure and a convenient reference for yourself, ensuring all critical information is accessible even if you lose your phone or documents while traveling.'
  }
];</parameter>
